values: So I am trying to figure out the whole journaling thing...and I am playing around with all of the features.  I realized that I don't have any pictures to put on my page, but if a certain current Floridian friend of mine would happen to e-mail me some current pictures from my recent visit, I might be able to find one :)  hint, hint :)

So here I am...An official Livejournal member...all because of my friend Cap'n.  I am only signing up for this so I can keep more updated on his really interesting social life....So here's to you Cap'n.... I am waiting to hear all of your fun stories :)
